reviews.text: Brunch buffet on Sunday.  Food quality very good.  Must try the caviar scallops.  The place is a bit crowded.

This place is quite good with a very diverse selections of food.   From Chinese to Indian to seafood. The quality of foods are quite good also.  My personal favorite is the desert department.  All their deserts are very nice and not too sweet.  Service is on point.  Please be sure to make reservation because this place gets very busy.

Friendly staff, food choices are acceptable with the price. But the food details such as tastes/textures and soup noodle portion can be further improved.(cold toppings)

Although the staff are quick and efficient in removing used plates off the tables, but I would suggest them try to do that in a more concealed manner. Try not to roam from table to table and hunt for finished plates to collect...

As for parking, the 3hr complementary valet parking is nicely done there.

I would visit again for family gathering, but not for business purposes because the atmosphere doesn't fit.
Very good breakfast buffet and wonderful service. Loved the matcha panecakes.

Good choice of food and i like the way the food is presented, a bit like in a market. They could improve even more by getting rid of the outdoor area and making it a central market with sitting area around it.

reviews.text: 自助餐很多榴槤甜品👍🏾
食物good👍👍👍👍
榴槤食品有特色👍

Hotel Icon自助餐最近主打台灣主題，兩星期限定的鹵肉飯香而不膩、烤地瓜甜而無渣、紅燒牛肉面藥燉湯底純厚。
但最吸晴的，要數這裡的招牌榴槤甜品—十款選擇包括榴槤布丁、榴槤蛋糕卷、榴槤糯米糕、榴槤冰淇淋等等！還有明爐蜜汁叉燒、馬來喇沙、汽鍋椰子燉雞湯、魚子醬吐司，都是一定一定要吃的
每次去都保持一貫水準，氣氛、食物質素。都能令人賓至如歸。如果對長者/小孩都可以給予優惠。就更貼心。♥️

reviews.text:
Well Done on their wine pairing with the truffle eggs and truffle shrimps. Wine pricing is 10-15% less than normal hotel. Friendly service, recommend to try. 

6pm - 8pm daily is normally for their club guests and not serving walk-in (I recommend they should consider 5pm - 7pm instead ☺️)

Great hotel very polite and helpful staff. Hotel is very environmentally aware as limousine and buses are electric, all bathroom items are plastic free. Level of service is great, mini bar is free and access is provided, via a phone, to mobile internet and it allows you to call home free. Food is excellent.  Really enjoyed my stay

Hotel Icon was amazing! Jessica made our stay even more special by greeting us with champagne and providing helpful tips for our stay. It was also so great to have a nice gym in the hotel that offered all of the equipment needed. I'd love to come back!

Located in heart of Hong Kong, Hotel Icon offered nice view to the harbour which is awesome. Easy access to everywhere. The services is great, all staff welcoming nicely and so helpfully.  They also have tea time which is super cute and delicious. The food was great, however on the Gala Dinner, the chicken bit rare.

Beautiful and modern.  Great room view of the harbor and amenities.   Free mini bar which is restocked every day.   Also, a Handy cell phone that is free to borrow.  You can use it to tour the city, and make local and international phone calls!!! 🙂
